a.n: Superfight Series Hungary, Hungary vs. China, Keckesmet, Hungary 12.10.2019

p.d: EM Legend 40 & Superfight Series Hungary: Hungary Station event. The debut in Europe of EM Legend organisation. Presented in association with Superfight Series Hungary on October 12th, 2019 in Keckmeset, Hungary. Fetatured five EM Legend stars facing Hungarian counterparts. Fightcard featured between others "Iron Blood" Pu Dongdong vs. Gabor Gorbics and Chen Zijun vs. Zoltan Nardelott.
